project_descr: At the request of the MoH, UNDP procures a range of medicines and medical products as an emergency measure, and builds the capacity needed to support a transparent, cost-effective procurement system for the Ministry.

outputs.output_descr: National health care procurement system strengthened and the effectiveness of diagnosis and treatment of the patients of Ukraine improved
